// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-0075 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: efab270e-5af6-5e67-b77c-f2e62ad7c020

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*amazonlinux:1*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:12.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:12.10*")
